data.description: LIKE NEW 4 BEDROOM HOME IN NORTH CLEVELAND - This stunning home is in immaculate condition and waiting for you to move in. The foyer guides you into the spacious living room with hardwood floors, gas fireplace, and tall vaulted ceiling and plantation shutters throughout. Mealtime is a breeze in this kitchen with granite counters, tile backsplash and stainless appliances, while entertaining and gathering can be held in formal dining room. The main level suite is a true retreat with a tile walk-in shower, soaking tub and walk-in closet. Upstairs, three bedrooms and a full bathroom provide you with privacy you crave. A covered patio overlooks the fenced backyard serving as a great spot for barbecues or enjoying your morning coffee. The outside of this home has been immaculately kept with an irrigation system and new gutter guards. Situated just moments from all Cleveland has to offer, this beautiful home won't last long!
